This is an online tool to help you with any time you want to host a sing
or karoake. You can paste the lyrics in here from any website where
they're written, and choose your preferred background color and
Once you start the song, the first line will be highlighted. Once you
sing that line, you can highlight the next line with your keyboard arrows.
You can then screen share to any big screen. This website also supports
Chromecast so you can share even if you're on a phone!
